    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add the <strong>rinsed red lentils</strong> to the pan with 700ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[1L]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and the <strong>vegetable stock mix </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 12-15 min or until the lentils are tender</p>",
